messages.message: Uploaded patch set 2: Patch Set 1 was rebased.
Uploaded patch set 3: Patch Set 2 was rebased.

Abandoned

We decided to give up on this change and keep the submittability expression always required. The reasoning is that users may override parts of the SR in the child project, e.g. by only defining an override expression. Since child does not define a submittability expression, it's explicitly always fulfilled without the user probably noticing this. 

More in https://gerrit-review.googlesource.com/c/gerrit/+/324036
